data.description: Do not miss this beauty in The Woods of West Creek.  It includes 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a formal living, separate dining, large open gourmet island kitchen and breakfast area off the family room with fireplace.  As you ascend the staircase you will find a large open game room ready for entertaining, all bedrooms and 2 baths.  The Spacious Primary Bedroom includes a master bath with separate tub and shower, double vanities and a master closet to die for.  The deck and patio are a great area for entertaining on those warm summer evenings and includes a large covered deck area, with large screen TX, and Hot Tub.  This beautiful home is surrounded in the back yard with many majestic Oaks and backs to a greenbelt.  Easy access to 1604 East and West, shopping and schools.  Come visit this beautiful home in The Woods of West Creek.
